54 Years of Friendship and Joy
       I am also so, so grateful for the 54 years of friendship and joy we
       shared. The pumps, the chess games, the construction work, the
       meals, the pranks, the life lessons - we did it all together. I
       will always miss you Franco.
       LEARN MORE
     * [00-bb-all-stars2.jpg]

Transforming Lives After School
       After-School All-Stars provides comprehensive after-school programs
       that keep children safe and help them succeed in school and life.
       VISIT WEBSITE
     * [00-bb-banner_bush.jpg]

Statement on the Passing of President George H.W. Bush
       From the day he first put on his U.S. Navy flight suit and took off
       into the unknown, he always put his country first. George Bush was
       an inspiration to all Americans and we will miss him dearly.
       READ MORE
     * [00-bb-banner_LG4.jpg]

Call to Action: War for Fair Districts
       While I am disappointed that the Supreme Court has chosen not to
       decide on the merits of extreme partisan gerrymandering for now, it
       is not the end of the war for fair districts. It is a call to
       action.
       LEARN MORE
     * [00-bb-banner_LG2.jpg]

Statement by Governor Schwarzenegger on the Passing of Barbara Bush
       My thoughts are with President Bush and the entire Bush family,
       along with every person on this planet who was lucky enough to call
       Barbara a friend.
       LEARN MORE

